news.title: Seal illegal structures even if notices issued: Telangana HC to GHMC
news.para: Justice B Vijaysen Reddy passed this interim order while hearing petition filed by Jijjuvarapu Ramesh who brought to the court's notice one such flagrant violation in OU Colony, Shaikpet wherein a person took permission from GHMC to construct stilt plus two floors but went on raising more floors.

news.title: New housing projects to be launched soon in 12 districts of Uttar Pradesh
news.para: "The CM was informed that under the Mukhyamantri Urban Expansion/New City Promotion Scheme, the approved projects will be launched in phases between June and December 2025," an official statement said.

news.title: Delhi HC seeks CBI reply on plea to probe corruption allegations in shopping mall's operations
news.para: ​Justice Girish Kathpalia issued notice to the Central Bureau of Investigation (CBI) on the petition which also sought registration of an FIR under the provisions of the Prevention of Corruption Act and the criminal penal law.
